import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title='About Me'
  description='Software Engineer passionate about building scalable systems'
  pubDate={new Date('February 13 2026')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}>
  <p>
    Hi! I'm <strong>Tomas</strong>, a software engineer with a passion for building robust, scalable systems and writing clean, maintainable
    code. I specialize in backend development, system architecture, and modern web technologies.
  </p>

  <h2>What I Do</h2>

  <p>
    My work focuses on designing and implementing software solutions that solve real-world problems. I believe in writing code that not only
    works but is also easy to understand, test, and maintain. Throughout my career, I've worked with various technologies and frameworks,
    always keeping an eye on best practices and emerging trends in software engineering.
  </p>

  <h2>This Website</h2>

  <p>
    <strong>TomasCodes.dev</strong> serves two purposes:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Portfolio:</strong> Showcasing my professional work, projects, and technical expertise</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Blog:</strong> Sharing knowledge, insights, and lessons learned throughout my engineering journey</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Topics I Write About</h2>

  <p>On this blog, you'll find articles covering a wide range of software engineering topics including:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>System design and architecture</li>
    <li>Backend development best practices</li>
    <li>Web technologies and frameworks</li>
    <li>Code quality and maintainability</li>
    <li>DevOps and deployment strategies</li>
    <li>Problem-solving approaches and debugging techniques</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Get In Touch</h2>

  <p>
    I'm always interested in connecting with fellow engineers, discussing technology, or exploring new opportunities. Feel free to reach out
    through the social links in the footer or check out my projects on GitHub.
  </p>
</Layout>
